Description copied from interface: SleeTransactionManager
Executes logic to complete the handling of a slee transaction by a method that requires a tx context. to be used as a complement of requireTransaction()

Parameters:
terminateTx - indicates if the logic should terminate the tx or not
doRollback - if true indicates a rollback should be done, either by terminating the tx with rollback() or by just setting the rollback only flag
